New Records: Niclas Fullkrug scored his 11th international goal in just 15 appearances
Key Match Events: Joey Veerman scored for the Netherlands in the 4th minute
Maximilian Mittelstadt equalized for Germany in the 10th minute
Niclas Fullkrug scored the winner for Germany in the final quarter
Post-Match Reflections: Julian Nagelsmann praised his team's performance and said they are well on track for Euro 2024
Ronald Koeman expressed disappointment with his team's finishing
Miscellaneous Highlights: Jamal Musiala was the brightest spark on the pitch, displaying his wide range of skills
Kai Havertz was an almost anonymous figure and was replaced in the 73rd minute
Others: The match was played at Frankfurt, Germany
The Netherlands will play Canada on June 6 in a warm-up friendly ahead of the European Championship
